result.deskripsine: With this add-on add to your Minecraft the characters of the video game Among Us where you can search who is the impostor, you can get as a skin a crew member of one color.

I have been playing Among Us recently, and its a fun game!
But, not all of my friends have it.

 But they do have Minecraft!
So this is the result of when 4 people are really bored in quarantine!

This map is based on the game Among Us.

 It has only THE SKELD map.

This map is also playable you can be CREWMATE or the IMPOSTOR.

 And here you can do tasks like scanning at the medbay and clicking the buttons on the diamond block.

Enjoying the grate game among us.

Love destroying your friendships as well as others but also love the blocky world of Minecraft.

Well here is the world of among us in Minecraft for all you amazing gamers to play.
